想我们肯定愿意这样做。我确信我们正在（与格拉斯顿伯里）进行谈判，如果没有，我们也会这样做。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Duran Duran 谈新音乐《Wet Leg》和他们的格拉斯顿伯里梦想 |谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-B-IVaTCP3k?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>然而，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-announced-as-headliners-of-latitude-festival-2024-3530450">将在今年的 Latitude Festival 上亮相，</a>并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondie">Blondie</a>和 Interpol 一起参加加利福尼亚州的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-interpol-blondie-headline-cruel-world-festival-2024-3553447">Cruel World Festival</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/interpol">。</a></p><p>他们还将与一系列其他名字一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kraftwerk-the-national-raye-pj-harvey-lead-massive-montreux-jazz-festival-2024-line-up-3619513">在蒙特勒爵士音乐节上亮相</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kraftwerk">Kraftwerk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">Raye</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alice-cooper">Alice Cooper</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessie-ware">Jessie Ware</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/air">Air</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lenny-kravitz">Lenny Kravitz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">Sting</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janelle-monae">Janelle Monáe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paolo-nutini">Paolo Nutini</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-cell">Soft Cell</a>等。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/duran-duran-delete-photo-with-tesla-cybertruck-after-online-backlash-3759442">杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 在网上强烈反对后删除了一张与特斯拉 Cyber​​truck 的照片。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-model-from-duran-durans-rio-cover-has-finally-been-identified-3764932">杜兰·杜兰 (Duran Duran) 的“里约”封面模特终于被确定的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
